# --- Repo-root safety net (the real rules live in soc-central/.gitignore) ---

# Personal Claude Code / IDE tooling config — not a project deliverable.
.claude/

# Secrets — never publish (belt-and-suspenders; also ignored in soc-central/).
.env
**/.env
!**/.env.example

# Study-only reference clones (~1 GB, junctioned to D:). Never commit.
reference/
**/reference/

# Local data volumes / build artifacts
**/data/
**/volumes/
__pycache__/
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
